{"title_page": "Florian Klein", "text_new": "{{Use dmy dates|date=April 2020}}\n{{Infobox football biography            \n| name = Florian Klein\n| image = AUT vs. TUR 2016-03-29 (080).jpg\n| image_size = 240\n| caption = Klein in 2016\n| height = {{height|m=1.80}}\n| birth_date = {{birth date and age|df=yes|1986|11|17}}\n| birth_place = [[Linz]], [[Upper Austria]], [[Austria]] \n| currentclub = [[FK Austria Wien|Austria Wien]]\n| clubnumber = 17\n| position = [[Defender (association football)|Defender]] \n| youthyears1 =   1994\u20132004\n| youthclubs1 =   [[LASK Linz]]\n| years1 =  2004\u20132009 \n| years2 =  2003\u20132004 \n| years3 =  2009\u20132012\n| years4 = 2012\u20132014\n| years5 = 2014\u20132017\n| years6 = 2017\u2013\n| clubs1 =   [[LASK Linz]] \n| clubs2 =  \u2192 [[FC Blau-Wei\u00df Linz]] (loan)\n| clubs3 =  [[FK Austria Wien|Austria Wien]]\n| clubs4 = [[FC Red Bull Salzburg|Red Bull Salzburg]]\n| clubs5 = [[VfB Stuttgart]]\n| clubs6 =  [[FK Austria Wien|Austria Wien]]\n| caps1 = 163  \n| caps2 = 19  \n| caps3 = 71\n| caps4 = 43\n| caps5 = 75\n| caps6 = 53\n| goals1 = 13  \n| goals2 = 5  \n| goals3 = 6\n| goals4 = 1\n| goals5 = 4\n| goals6 = 5\n| nationalyears1 = 2005\u20132006 \n| nationalyears2 = 2006\u20132008\n| nationalyears3 = 2010\u2013\n| nationalteam1 =  [[Austria national under-19 football team|Austria U19]] \n| nationalteam2 =  [[Austria national under-21 football team|Austria U21]]\n| nationalteam3 =  [[Austria national football team|Austria]]\n| nationalcaps1 =  5  \n| nationalcaps2 =  23 \n| nationalcaps3 =  45\n| nationalgoals1 = 0   \n| nationalgoals2 = 3 \n| nationalgoals3 = 0\n| manageryears1 =   \n| managerclubs1 =   \n| club-update = 16:36, 29 September 2017 (UTC)\n| nationalteam-update = 15 November 2016\n}}\n\n'''Florian Klein''' (born 17 November 1986) is an Austrian [[Association football|footballer]] who currently plays as a [[Defender (association football)|defender]] for [[FK Austria Wien|Austria Wien]].\n\n==Career==\nKlein began his career in September 1994 in the youth team of [[LASK Linz]] and was promoted to the senior team in July 2004.<ref>[http://lask.at/content/lask/team/profis LASK-Profile] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070927143746/http://lask.at/content/lask/team/profis |date=27 September 2007 }}</ref> He played on loan for [[FC Blau-Wei\u00df Linz]] in the 2003\u201304 season and returned to Linz after the end of the season. After 163 games in 14 years for the club, in which he scored 13 goals, Klein signed a two-year contract with [[FK Austria Wien|Austria Wien]] on 30 April 2009. In 2012, he joined [[FC Red Bull Salzburg|Red Bull Salzburg]].<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://redbulls.com/soccer/salzburg/de/Florian-Klein.html |title=Archived copy |access-date=8 July 2012 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120908173910/http://redbulls.com/soccer/salzburg/de/Florian-Klein.html |archive-date=8 September 2012 |url-status=dead }}</ref>\n\nAfter the end of his contract with Salzburg on 1 July 2014, Klein moved to [[VfB Stuttgart]] on a [[Bosman ruling|free transfer]]. On 6 May 2014, Florian Klein signed a contract until June 2017 with VfB Stuttgart.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.vfb.de/en/aktuell/meldungen/news/2014/transfer-florian-klein/page/3014-1-1-.html|title=VfB sign Florian Klein|work=vfb.de|publisher=[[VfB Stuttgart]]|date=6 May 2014|accessdate=6 May 2014|url-status=dead|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140506200322/http://www.vfb.de/en/aktuell/meldungen/news/2014/transfer-florian-klein/page/3014-1-1-.html|archivedate=6 May 2014}}</ref>\n\nHe returned to [[FK Austria Wien|Austria Wien]] on 23 August 2017.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.fk-austria.at/de/n/news/2017/08/florian-klein-kehrt-zur-austria-zurueck/|title=Florian Klein kehrt zur Austria zur\u00fcck|publisher=[[FK Austria Wien]]|date=23 August 2017|access-date=23 August 2017|language=de}}</ref>\n\n==International career==\nKlein has played for Austria under-19 and Austria under-21. On 19 May 2010, Klein made his debut for the [[Austria national football team|Austria]] against [[Croatia national football team|Croatia]].{{citation needed|date=October 2015}}\n\n==Career statistics==\n{{updated|1 July 2019.}}\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align: center\"\n|-\n!rowspan=\"2\"|Club!!rowspan=\"2\"|Season!!colspan=\"3\"|League!!colspan=\"2\"|Cup{{ref|a|1}}!!colspan=\"2\"|Continental{{ref|a|2}}!!colspan=\"2\"|Other!!colspan=\"2\"|Total!!rowspan=\"2\"|{{Tooltip|Ref.|Reference}}\n|-\n!League!!Apps!!Goals!!Apps!!Goals!!Apps!!Goals!!Apps!!Goals!!Apps!!Goals\n|-\n|rowspan=\"6\"|[[LASK Linz|Linz]]||[[2004\u201305 Austrian Football First League|2004\u201305]]||rowspan=\"3\"|[[Austrian Football First League|First League]]||29||0||2||0||colspan=\"2\"|\u2014||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||31||0||<ref name=\"wf\">{{cite web|title=wf|url=http://www.worldfootball.net/player_summary/florian-klein/2/|website=Worldfootball.net|accessdate=10 October 2014}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[2005\u201306 Austrian Football First League|2005\u201306]]||35||1||1||0||colspan=\"2\"|\u2014||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||36||1||<ref name=\"wf\"/>\n|-\n|[[2006\u201307 Austrian Football First League|2006\u201307]]||32||5||3||0||colspan=\"2\"|\u2014||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||35||5||<ref name=\"wf\"/>\n|-\n|[[2007\u201308 Austrian Football Bundesliga|2007\u201308]]||rowspan=\"2\"|[[Austrian Football Bundesliga|Austrian Bundesliga]]||34||1||colspan=\"2\"|\u2014||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||colspan=\"2\"|\u2014||34||1||<ref name=\"wf\"/>\n|-\n|[[2008\u201309 Austrian Football Bundesliga|2008\u201309]]||33||5||2||0||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||colspan=\"2\"|\u2014||35||5||<ref name=\"wf\"/>\n|-\n!colspan=\"2\"|Totals!!163!!12!!8!!0!!0!!0!!0!!0!!171!!12!!\u2014\n|-\n|rowspan=\"4\"|[[FK Austria Wien|Austria Wien]]||[[2009\u201310 FK Austria Wien season|2009\u201310]]||rowspan=\"3\"|Austrian Bundesliga||35||4||3||0||10||0||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||48||4||<ref name=\"wf\"/>\n|-\n|[[2010\u201311 FK Austria Wien season|2010\u201311]]||36||